      %p
        Once again, expectations can be high when you have reached your chosen holiday destination and why not?
        You have spent your hard earned cash on booking some quality downtime and you want it to be filled with more fun than hassle and to go extremely smoothly, so it’s important to do a little beach bag ‘thinking ahead’ before you leave.
        Let's take a quick look at what it is that we expect from our hard working beach bag on our annual summer vay-cay?

      %p
        Here are some key essential components for any holiday beach bag.
        Taking a minute to look at these now will save you from bad choices or forgotten items whilst you are away so your time in the sun is hassle free and all you dreamed of.

