      %p
        When the sun is up you want to be out there making the most of it.
        Constantly unpacking and repacking your beach bag and searching for that essential item, when all you want to do is enjoy the beach can be frustrating.
        So don’t forget your unique key items too.
        We all have different and personal needs unique to us. So, these are the things that you personally cannot do without during your time on the beach.
      
      %p
        Here is my unique list:

        %ol
          %li
            %span.strong
              Beach dress or shirt 
            \– to cover up if it gets a bit too hot or for when I am walking about
          %li
            %span.strong
              Hat 
            \– in case my head starts gets a bit too hot and to protect my scalp from the sun
          %li
            %span.strong
